</li><li> Jix was thought to be male until her brother Romulos revealed her true identity (it's hard to tell what gender a small furry alien is unless you are able to see anything).
</li></ul></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/AModestDestiny" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/AModestDestiny">A Modest Destiny</a></em>:
<ul><li> <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">Shadow</span> spends a good amount of time in the comics as this until an incident where Maxim <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThanksForTheMammaries" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThanksForTheMammaries">grabbed her</a> <a class="urllink" href="http://www.squidi.net/comic/amd/view.php?ep=1=100">breast<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>, and it's not shown who she is until much later.
